description: Number of partitions satisfying (cn(0,5) = 0 and cn(2,5) <= cn(1,5) and cn(3,5) <= cn(1,5) and cn(2,5) <= cn(4,5) and cn(3,5) <= cn(4,5)).
comments: For a given partition cn(i,n) means the number of its parts equal to i modulo n.Short: (0 := 0 and 2<=1 and 3<=1 and 2<=4 and 3<=4).
